sentences: Elizabeth Davis-Simpson (born December 18, 1965 in the United States), is best known for being an American songwriter, as well as the bassist of the punk rock band 7 Year Bitch.
She later worked on projects such as These Streets with Valerie Agnew, and has participated in a band named Clone.
